title: Week 6 preview & Broncos vs Chargers recap
itunes:title: Week 6 preview & Broncos vs Chargers recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game recapping each week 6 matchup. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night AFC West showdown between the Denver Broncos and the San Diego Chargers.
